        <span class="ph-eyebrow">Our Story</span>
        <h1 class="ph-title">Luxury Fragrance, Made <em>Honest</em></h1>
        <p class="ph-sub">The Fragrance Secrets was born from a simple frustration — that authentic luxury perfume in the UAE was either overpriced or impossible to trust. We set out to change both: genuine fragrances, fair prices, and a promise you can verify on every bottle.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta">
          <span><span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">verified_user</span>100% Authentic</span>
          <span><span class="mi" aria-hidden="true">storefront</span>218+ Brands</span>
