    <!-- BRAND STORY — ORIGINS / HERITAGE / INSPIRATION -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="about-split container">
        <figure class="about-figure fade-up">
          <img src="{{ 'prod-bouquet-oud.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Curated luxury fragrance bottles" />
        </figure>
        <div class="about-body fade-up">
          <span class="label">Where It Began</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title">A House Built on <em>Trust</em></h2>
          <p>We started in 2019 as a small team of fragrance lovers in Dubai, tired of watching friends and family pay designer money for bottles they couldn't be sure were real. The counterfeit problem in the region was open knowledge — but nobody was solving it with both authenticity and accessibility in mind.</p>
          <p>So we built the store we wished existed. Every fragrance we list is sourced through verified channels, checked batch by batch, and priced to be genuinely fair — never inflated because it carries a luxury name. From rich Arabic oud to designer classics and modern niche, our shelves are curated with one filter: would we wear it, and would we gift it?</p>
          <p>Today, that same obsession with authenticity guides everything — from the houses we partner with to the way our team answers a WhatsApp message at 6pm on a weekday.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COMMITMENT FEATURE — AUTHENTICITY & QUALITY -->
    <section class="section alt">
