          <span class="label">Our Commitment</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title">Authenticity Is Not a <em>Feature</em></h2>
          <p>For us, authenticity isn't a badge we add at checkout — it's the reason the company exists. Alongside verified resale of the world's designer and Arabic houses, we craft our own labels: Fragrance Secrets, Secret Scents and the Paris Collection — created in the UAE, for the UAE.</p>
          <p>Every product passes through our verification process before it reaches you, and every order is backed by 7-day returns, free delivery over AED 150, and cash on delivery across all seven Emirates. If something isn't right, our team makes it right — no scripts, no run-around.</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px">
